{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I could see a large number of barracks-- small, one-story barracks inside the prison compound that housed the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Well, they came streaming out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They had finally realized what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And they screamed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they shouted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they started tossing bodies through the air.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I was just stunned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I-- for a moment, I couldn't figure out what was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Because there were thousands of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "It turned out there was about almost 32,000 in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And the ones that were still able to walk around [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were tossing these bodies over their outstretched hands.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they were tearing at them with their hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I immediately said to my interpreter, ask this guy, this prisoner who is with us, what's going on in there?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They talked in German for a few seconds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- my interpreter said, well, Colonel, he said they're killing the informers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the word he used to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we were helpless to do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it quieted down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to start yelling at them in German and tell them that they have to remain here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we'll get food, medicine, up to them as rapidly as we can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they are not to try to get out of the compound.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I could see I didn't want to have prisoners running all over the area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were still in combat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Besides, I-- most of them were desperately ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it quieted down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was yelling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The company then, we started encircling the whole area and taking over the guard towers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it got very quiet there for a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the prisoners were just-- inside the compound, were just standing there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very listlessly.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
